<br>
The Berzerker's frenzy ability has been stripped of its negative side-effects, and instead has been given a self-buff which doubles the target's AF for 30 seconds. This is to compensate for the 10pt cost Mercenary RA, Cheap Shot. Previously, mercenaries were using this realm ability on flipped out trolls in order to deal &quot;large amounts of damage&quot;. This was never intended to be the case. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#000000>- </font><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc>Light Tanks of DAoC</a><font color=#000000> - </font><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2>Mercenary General Discussion</a> <font color=#000000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.245d<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

